Name: Critical Force Test
Description: The classical critical force test. 7 sec on, 3 sec off for 4 minutes in total. Pull as hard as you can.

Name: Max Hangs 90%
Description: The goal of this workout is to improve forearm and fingerstrength. Use 90% of your total load score on a 20mm edge.

Name: Anaerobic Capacity 80%
Description: Deadhang repeaters. 7 sec hang, 3 sec rest at 80%.

Name: Test Workout
Description: Simple test workout. No weight, 15sec dead hang on 20mm edge, 1min Pause. 4 Sets.

Name: Anaerobic Capacity 70%
Description: Deadhang repeaters. 7 sec hang, 3 sec rest at 70%.

Name: Density Hangs 70%
Description: Long duration dead hangs. 30 second hangs at 70%.
